teagle.repository

Class ResourceInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • teagle.repository.ResourceInstance

  • public class ResourceInstance
extends Object
    Class to model the representation of specific instances of resources within the repository. For example, given a resource type for an Apache HTTP server with 3 available servers for booking, each of them would be an instance of this class.
    Author:
    alexandru.mihaiuc@fokus.fraunhofer.de
